终端
1. 安装指令（国内镜像版） 
/bin/zsh -c "$(curl -fsSL https://gitee.com/cunkai/HomebrewCN/raw/master/Homebrew.sh)"
2. 写入配置文件指令
echo 'eval "$(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv zsh)"' >> /Users/hongchen/.zprofile
3. 立即激活指令
eval "$(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv zsh)"
4.安装python
brew install python
5.查询python是否安装成功
python3 --version
